_:N450ee74116094178a824421f09f939d7 <http://schema.org/name> "The Rt Hon James Murray MP" .
<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/james-murray> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://schema.org/WebPage> .
_:N450ee74116094178a824421f09f939d7 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>James Murray has served as the Member of Parliament for Ealing North since 2019.</p>\n\n<p>He was appointed Secretary of State for Health and Social Care on 14 May 2026. He was previously Chief Secretary to the Treasury from 1 September 2025 to 14 May 2026. He previously held the office of Exchequer Secretary to the Treasury, having been shadow Financial Secretary for three and a half years before that.</p>\n\n<p>He is a member of the Labour and Co-operative parties and served as the Deputy Mayor of London for Housing and Residential Development from 2016 to 2019.</p>\n\n<p>Prior to being appointed Deputy Mayor, he served as a councillor for a decade, including six years as executive member for housing and development from 2010 to 2016.</p>\n\n<p>Earlier in his career, he worked in a management consultancy.</p>\n" .
